{"tid":1788252,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［英國旗］王婆婆報平安 自製聖誕卡 籲香港人Be Safe","createTime":"2019-12-18T13:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-18T15:25:03.000Z","uid":8968,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d94a26e1ba02d76134fa05e871abcffd65146c33","tid":1788252,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:48:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/asdXZiM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FasdXZiM.png&h=3b885f87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家集會遊行成日會見到揮英國旗嘅「王婆婆」王鳳瑤，8月於太古警方清場行動中被帶走之後，曾經幾個月時間音訊全無，令唔少港人擔心。臨近聖誕，雖然仲未見到王婆婆露面，但近日有社運界人士就收到佢嘅報平安E-mail，並附上自製電子聖誕卡祝福香港人，十分窩心。<br />\n<br />\n上月臨近區議會選舉，王婆婆曾經以電郵回覆《立場新聞》，提到佢當時喺深圳取保候審，每晚噩夢係重回看守所，而自己一張選票化作廢紙，呼籲港人代為加油，記得要監票留守。<br />\n<br />\n而今次電郵，王婆婆就寫上「I am not bad」報平安，又表示衷心祝福所有香港人，附上一張自製嘅聖誕卡，畫有聖誕樹、笑笑口嘅黃傘，又寫有「民主、人權、自由」等願望，以及「Be Safe」。<br />\n<br />\n對上一次王婆婆公開露面，係8月11日港島東大遊行，夜晚警方清場時，王婆婆喺太古港鐵站C出口外被警員帶離現場，自此缺席所有示威行動。"},{"pid":"1a03d94443ab5ad8669cd0fa5d0968e4e5b82ac7","tid":1788252,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:49:11.000Z","msg":"連黑警老母都睇過既文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1787578/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1787578/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6nvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=fb34bb30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"c9168e2fed4e95a07e9b0f422cd38b6b3b3e8ec5","tid":1788252,"uid":326427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-18T13:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0aMiJK3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0aMiJK3.jpg&h=7645b339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n［同我推上熱門］［行動］平安夜要經濟攬炒呀！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1786709\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1786709</a